data.description: Looking for a charming, farmhouse chic one-story home with two bedrooms and two bathrooms that's close to the East River Development? Look no further than this stunning single family home!  Built recently and surrounded by other new construction in the area, this home offers modern amenities and plenty of space for you and your family. Inside, you'll find high-end finishes and features, including high end flooring and stainless steel appliances.  The open-concept layout is perfect for entertaining, with a spacious kitchen that flows seamlessly into the dining area and living room.  The master suite is a true retreat, with a spa-like bathroom and ample closet space. The second bedroom and bathroom provide plenty of space for guests.  With the East River Development just a short distance away, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options.  Schedule a showing today!
